extendedInfo.description: Get a Christian perspective! If you want solid Christian spiritual dating advice, seek out material by and for Christians.

reviews.title: What...?
reviews.comment: Could not uninstall fast enough.  The first entry took me to some travel website which promptly froze up, and the second entry is a short generic essay about not compromising one\'s Christian values and standing strong in the current culture.  That\'s it.  I was hoping for some in-depth, practical tips or strategies in how to be a man of God pertaining to dating.  Extremely disappointing.
reviews.author: A Google User
